transcript:
Agent: Hi, my name is John and I'm calling from GreenTech. How are you today?
Customer: I'm doing well, thanks. Who is this and how did you get my number?
Agent: We obtained your contact information from a trade show you attended last month. I'm calling to introduce you to our energy-efficient lighting solutions.
Customer: Okay, I remember attending that show. What makes your products so special?
Agent: Our LED bulbs last up to 50% longer than competitors and use significantly less energy.
Customer: That sounds interesting. We're actually looking to replace our current lighting system soon.
Agent: Great timing! Our products can help you reduce your energy consumption and save on costs in the long run.
Customer: How much do they cost?
Agent: Our prices start at $15 per bulb, but we're currently offering a discount for bulk orders.
Customer: Okay, that's a bit higher than what we're used to paying. What kind of support do you offer?
Agent: We provide a 5-year warranty and dedicated customer service team to ensure a smooth transition.
Customer: Alright, I'd like to learn more. Can you send me some more information and a quote?
Agent: Absolutely, I'll send you an email with all the details. Would you like to schedule a follow-up call to discuss further?
Customer: Yes, that would be great. How about next Wednesday?
Agent: Sounds good. I'll make sure to schedule it. Is there anything else you'd like to know before we wrap up?
Customer: No, that's all for now. Thanks for the information, John.
Agent: You're welcome. I look forward to speaking with you next Wednesday.
Customer: Me too, thanks.
Agent: Have a great day and I'll talk to you soon.
Customer: You too, bye.
